href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03882-HK</a>)</td><td>0.890</td><td>-5.32</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>思摩爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06969:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06969\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06969-HK</a>)</td><td>19.860</td><td>-6.32</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>麗年國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09918:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09918\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09918-HK</a>)</td><td>1.180</td><td>-28.48</td><td></td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
