            "title": "《大手成交》恒生中國企業一手50萬股非自動對盤,涉4522萬",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社1日專訊》恒生中國企業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02828:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02828\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02828-HK</a>)於3:20pm錄得1手50萬股非自動對盤,每股造90.45元,較上日收市價低0.5%,涉資4522萬元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　恒生中國企業現價跌0.7%,報90.28元;成交5229萬股,成交金額47.47億元,主動買沽比率49:51,資金淨主動賣出4592萬元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
